</div>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">++&nbsp;Standard&nbsp;Item&nbsp;Containment&nbsp;Units</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">--&nbsp;Suggested&nbsp;by&nbsp;various&nbsp;users&nbsp;in&nbsp;chat!</a></div>
