<h2 id="toc12"><span><span style="color:#0044a3"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;</span>Standard Secure Locker Unit</span></span></h2>
<img src="http://fc02.deviantart.net/fs71/f/2014/329/5/5/ssl_1_by_alanthos-d87mnot.png" width="570px" alt="ssl_1_by_alanthos-d87mnot.png" class="image" />
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/search:site/a/pf/q/locker%20title:SCP">If I have to link you to every single time a Locker has been used in a SCP article, we'll never be done with this.</a></p>
