<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">--&nbsp;Suggested&nbsp;by&nbsp;various&nbsp;users&nbsp;in&nbsp;chat!</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<div style="float: center; border: double 2px #0044a3; width: 570px; padding: 1px 15px; margin: 10px 10px 10px 40px; background-color: #fff; box-shadow: 0 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,.2);">
<h2 id="toc13"><span><span style="color:#0044a3"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;</span>Standard Secure Chest</span></span></h2>
<img src="http://th08.deviantart.net/fs70/PRE/f/2014/357/9/b/ssc_01_by_alanthos-d8avxoh.png" width="570px" alt="ssc_01_by_alanthos-d8avxoh.png" class="image" />
<p style="text-align: center;">What, did you think the Foundation would carry <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/safe">Safe</a> and <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/log-of-anomalous-items">Anomalous</a> items by hand whenever they have to evacuate a Site?</p>
</div>
