<p style="text-align: center;">Not that it's entirely relevant in this case or in any case, since Randomini's tales are known to everybody&#8230; but in case you have somehow NOT read them yet, make a wiser use of your time and go to the <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/the-cool-war-hub">Cool War Hub</a> first.</p>
